    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>disease (injury); <strong>Save&nbsp;</strong>Fortitude DC 15;</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong>&nbsp;<span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDiseases_ctl00_LabelName\">1 day</span>;&nbsp;<strong>Frequency</strong>&nbsp;1/day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>1d3 Con damage and 1d3 Wis damage</p>\n<p><strong>Cure&nbsp;</strong>2 consecutive saves</p>\n<hr />\n<p>A humanoid afflicted with Moxix&rsquo;s delectation must attempt a new Will save each day. If the humanoid fails, it attacks and attempts to eat the weakest humanoid nearby. If the save is successful, it resists. A humanoid who dies or is killed while afflicted rises as a ghast at the next midnight. The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>",
